《'''-{zh-cn:破碎之家; zh-tw:愛的餘燼; zh-hk:傷失的情歌}-'''》（''The Broken Circle Breakdown''）是一部2012年[[菲力斯·冯·古宁根|菲力斯·冯·古宁根]]执导的[[比利时|比利时]]剧情片，根据 [[Johan_Heldenbergh|Johan Heldenbergh]] 所写的戏剧改编而成。它代表比利时角逐第86届[[奥斯卡最佳外语片|奥斯卡最佳外语片]]<ref name="Belgium">{{cite web |url=http://www.flandersimage.com/news/detail/the-broken-circle-breakdown-represents-belgium-at-foreign-language-oscars |title=The Broken Circle Breakdown represents Belgium at Foreign Language Oscars |accessdate=2013-09-23 |work=Flanders Image |archive-date=2015-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617041430/http://www.flandersimage.com/news/detail/the-broken-circle-breakdown-represents-belgium-at-foreign-language-oscars |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="HWR">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-belgium-nominates-broken-circle-635395 |title=Oscars: Belgium Nominates 'The Broken Circle Breakdown' for Foreign Language Category |accessdate=2013-09-24 |work=Hollywood Reporter |archive-date=2015-05-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150518013624/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-belgium-nominates-broken-circle-635395 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并最终获得提名。赢得[[欧洲电影奖|欧洲电影奖]]最佳女演员奖和第39届法国[[凯撒电影奖|凯撒电影奖]]最佳外语片。

== 剧情 ==
讲述一对夫妻因女儿患上[[癌症|癌症]]、接受治疗最终去世后，这个小家庭逐渐崩溃的过程，回忆穿插了两人在[[乐队|乐队]]交往相爱的经过。

